[SN]TITLE[SN]
'Major blaze' strikes derelict Kintore hotel

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Firefighters have been called to what is described as a "major blaze" at a derelict hotel in Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
At 23:30 on Monday the fire was discovered at the Torryburn Hotel in Kintore.
About 40 firefighters attended the incident.
The fire was reported to be under control by 04:00 on Tuesday.
